org.apache.ignite.ml.trainers.group

Interface Metaoptimizer<LC,X,Y,I,D,O>

  • Type Parameters:
    LC - Local context of GroupTrainer.
    X - Type of data which is processed in training loop step.
    Y - Type of data returned by training loop step data processor.
    I - Type of data to which data returned by distributed initialization is mapped.
    D - Type of data returned by initialization.
    O - Type of data to which data returned by data processor is mapped.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MLPMetaoptimizer

    public interface Metaoptimizer<LC,X,Y,I,D,O>
    Class encapsulating data transformations in group training in MetaoptimizerGroupTrainer, which is adapter of GroupTrainer.
